verbose_text: Previous studies by our group have demonstrated that PEDF protects cardiomyocytes against hypoxia induced apoptosis and necroptosis via anti-oxidative effects, and PEDF improves cardiac function in rats with acute myocardial infarction via inhibition of vascular permeability and cardiomyocyte apoptosis.
evidence: PEDF protects cardiomyocytes against hypoxia-induced apoptosis and necroptosis
